import React, { useEffect } from 'react' import { Icon, Label, Menu, Table } from 'semantic-ui-react' import HeaderForm from './HeaderForm' import BodyForm from './BodyForm' import uuid from 'react-uuid' function TableForm (props) { const data = props.data const listDolls = data.map(doll => {doll._id} {doll.name} {doll.priceBought} {doll.dateBought} {doll.sold} {doll.priceSold} {doll.dateSold} {doll.boughtBy} {doll.shippingAddress} ) return(
ID Name Price bought Date bought Sold Price sold Date sold Bought by Shipping address Options {listDolls}
) } export default TableForm
